"6:162:7" : {s: 6, a: 162, w: 7, r: "اله", t: "لِلَّهِ", l: "ٱللَّه", lc: 2811, tl: "lillahi", lb: "আল্লাহ",e: "(are) for Allah", b: "আল্লাহর জন্য/উদ্দেশ্যে", i: "untuk Allah", f: 102, rm: "to serve, worship or adore; to protect, grant refuge, preserve save, rescue, liberate; object of worship ie God; (ا-ل-ل-ه) God, the one true God applied as a proper name denoting the true god, comprising all the excellent divine names; a unity comprising all the essences of existing things."},
